data.message: Brand Expression System: 12 Jungian Archetypes (Innocent, Explorer, Sage, Hero, Outlaw, Magician, Regular Guy, Lover, Jester, Caregiver, Creator, Ruler) + Aaker's 5 Dimensions (Sincerity, Excitement, Competence, Sophistication, Ruggedness). Visual language mapping: Color psychology (blue=trust, red=energy, black=luxury), Typography personality (serif=traditional/trustworthy, sans=modern/clean, display=expressive), Shape language (circles=friendly, squares=stable, triangles=dynamic). Brand coherence requires consistent application across all touchpoints.
